verbose_text: Although HOXC10 expression in the entire TCGA-GBM group was not significantly correlated with VEGFA expression (n = 156, r = 0.146, P = 0.069), we found that HOXC10 expression in the PRMT5 higher-GBM subgroup was significantly correlated with VEGFA levels (n = 78, r = 0.279, P = 0.014), which further supported that PRMT5 contributes to HOXC10 mediated VEGFA upregulation.
